  <brief_title>FIrst Line Treatment of Metastatic Pancreatic Cancer: Sequential Nab-paclitaxel + Gemcitabine/FOLFIRI.3 VS Nab-paclitaxel + Gemcitabine</brief_title>
  <acronym>FIRGEMAX</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase II Randomised Multicenter Trial Evaluating a Sequential Treatment With Nab-paclitaxel+Gemcitabine /FOLFIRI.3 vs Nab-paclitaxel + Gemcitabine in First Line Metastatic Pancreatic Cancer</official_title>
