  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this trial is to evaluate every 2 months alternating
      nab-paclitaxel/gemcitabine and FOLFIRI.3 versus nab-paclitaxel + gemcitabine, regarding the
      progression of disease at 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
